    {
      "id": "detailed_3_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_3",
      "description": "This vehicle is in good condition and has been consistently well-maintained throughout its life. The engine and transmission operate smoothly, providing a dependable and responsive driving experience. While the interior and exterior show some minor signs of normal wear and tear, such as small surface scratches and light seat creasing, the car is mechanically sound and ready for its next owner. It has been recently serviced and is perfect for someone looking for a reliable, quality pre-owned vehicle.",
