    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_0_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "sybil_0",
      "description": "We are pleased to present this superlative vehicle, maintained to the highest standards of automotive excellence. This specimen remains in pristine condition, exhibiting a flawless exterior finish and an interior that retains its original showroom integrity. Meticulously preserved and mechanically beyond reproach, this motorcar represents a rare opportunity for the discerning buyer who demands uncompromised quality and an impeccable service history. Serious inquiries are invited for this investment-grade acquisition.",
      "price": 43900.0,
